lines.line: Meet Felix, the bodybuilder cat who trains every day to maintain his impressive physique.
After his gym caught fire last week, he made a daring escape that was captured on security cameras.
Now recovering from his ordeal, Felix spends his days hitting the books to learn about fire safety.
His inspiring story of resilience has made him a role model for other young cats who have survived similar disasters.
